properties.entry:
All of the CQ component and template definitions for the 'CQ Blueprints Example' project.
During development, the files in this module should be sync'd to your CQ instance using the FileVault command line tool available with CQ. There is also a plugin for Eclipse called "vaultclipse" that can be used instead of the command line tool.
It is recommended that this module not contain any Java code and instead Java code should be placed in either the PersonRegistry-taglib module or the PersonRegistry-services module as appropriate.
